WEBVTT

1
00:01:17.100 --> 00:01:21.200
<font color="#14ff0f">Las käia Layla. laula koos minuga.</font>

2
00:01:22.140 --> 00:01:23.440
<font color="#14ff0f">Ei.</font>

3
00:01:23.580 --> 00:01:25.580
