4
00:01:48.940 --> 00:01:51.540
<font color="#14ff0f">Sa paned mu pea valutama.</font>

5
00:01:55.064 --> 00:01:57.064
<font color="#14ff0f">Teie kõik.</font>

6
00:02:42.496 --> 00:02:43.496
