8
00:03:27.689 --> 00:03:29.689
<font color="#14ff0f">Lapsed...</font>

9
00:03:29.713 --> 00:03:31.713
<font color="#14ff0f">püsige siin.</font>

10
00:04:28.137 --> 00:04:30.737
<font color="#14ff0f">Kuidas me teame millal on aeg?</font>

11
00:04:33.961 --> 00:04:35.961
<font color="#14ff0f">Me jälgime.</font>

12
00:04:54.985 --> 00:04:57.185
<font color="#14ff0f">Tasem. natuke veel.</font>

13
00:05:39.109 --> 00:05:40.809
<font color="#14ff0f">On ta ärkvel?</font>

14
00:06:02.933 --> 00:06:04.933
<font color="#14ff0f">Ütle juba. on ta ärkvel?</font>

15
00:06:12.857 --> 00:06:14.857
<font color="#14ff0f">Jumal olgu tänatud.</font>

16
00:06:49.881 --> 00:06:56.181
<b>Lee Cronini Muumia</b>

17
00:07:24.878 --> 00:07:26.647
- Pepperonipitsa?

18
00:07:27.948 --> 00:07:29.617
Oled siin kõik ära korraldanud.

19
00:07:29.750 --> 00:07:31.151
Kas me saame täna pitsat?

20
00:07:31.284 --> 00:07:32.419
Täna mitte. semu.

21
00:07:32.553 --> 00:07:33.630
Sulle ei meeldi isegi pitsa.

22
00:07:33.654 --> 00:07:35.455
Ei. mulle ei meeldi juust.

23
00:07:35.823 --> 00:07:38.025
Pitsa pole pitsa ilma juustuta.

24
00:07:38.526 --> 00:07:40.260
Tal on õigus.

25
00:07:40.393 --> 00:07:41.705
Tehakse laiaulatuslikke
pingutusi...

26
00:07:41.729 --> 00:07:43.797
- Isa. tule nüüd. Veel üks.
- Jah...

27
00:07:44.064 --> 00:07:45.899
Olgu. Teeme...

28
00:07:46.033 --> 00:07:47.210
